description: This file defines a data class 'TeamSession' for managing team session data, including methods for serialization, deserialization, and telemetry data extraction.

classes.name: TeamSession
classes.description: A data class representing a team session stored in the database, with methods for converting to dict, extracting telemetry data, and creating an instance from a dict.

methods.name: to_dict
methods.description: Converts the TeamSession instance to a dictionary.

methods.name: telemetry_data
methods.description: Returns a dictionary with telemetry information such as model, creation, and update timestamps.

methods.name: from_dict
methods.description: Creates a TeamSession instance from a dictionary, with validation for session_id.
